            . I am a bird-fancier. This goat was on Mr. Chapman's premises, at the back of <placeName id="t18290409-266-crimeloc1498">Barnsbury-park. Islington</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18290409-266-crimeloc1498" type="placeName" value="Barnsbury-park. Islington"></interp>
