                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290409-266-off1496 t18290409-266-crimeloc1498"></join>, on the 11th of April; there is a bank round the field; the prisoner ran, took a strap from his pocket, and led the goat away - he took it into Maiden-lane, and the officer took him; I had not known him before.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290409-266-person2446">
                  WILLIAM 
                  BERNARD
